{"tid":1954524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有線新聞］中國收緊出口物資政策   商務部 ：我們沒有興趣為行善而遭受抺黑污衊","createTime":"2020-04-02T01:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T02:21:55.000Z","uid":186071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4f9639bb90863e22d2ec6079365880feb0e147","tid":1954524,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=22006&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.hkott.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D22006%26ct%3D1&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f3bfc533\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=22006&amp;ct=1</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】中國出口的醫療物資被指國際抨擊質量低劣，商務部隨即就有行動&mdash;&mdash;4月1日起，企業出口醫療物資，包括檢測試劑和口罩等，都要取得中國的註冊證書。<br />\n比起以往只要有美國FDA或歐盟CE認證就可以出口，新規下出口條件更嚴格。<br />\n商務部研究員梅新育強調，提高出口門檻是回應國際要求，屬自衛措施，「你自己沒有按照中國的產品使用說法去正確使用，不加查證就抺黑到中國產品的頭上。我們想用中國的生產能力挽救生命，我們想做善事，但是我們沒有興趣為行善而遭受抺黑污衊，那麼把它(出口要求)收緊一點，順你們的意吧。」<br />\n但有在山東生產防護服的商人認為，是當局之前監管不力，現在才要用新規回應國際質疑：「(中國)之前出了很多貨去歐洲那邊，確實是有FDA、CE的(認證)，但有部分廠家拿到認證後，實際上提供的產品是跟CE、FDA的檢測報告的產品質量不相符。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=22006&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fl.hkott.hk%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D22006%26ct%3D1&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f3bfc533\" target=\"_blank\">https://l.hkott.hk/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=22006&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"b796841b88c2d1c1679b98fd04de3c1eb0823fe0","tid":1954524,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:41:22.000Z","msg":"究竟做咩中國先會唔覺得人抹黑? 中國人係咪真係咁自卑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbea5e846d2f02dd534cdd937340807e56efbbb2","tid":1954524,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:42:51.000Z","msg":"做善事 賣十幾蚊一個口罩"},{"pid":"8e82bf04f91a5d797aab5dfa04313d87e6236549","tid":1954524,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"而家台灣講到明要同歐盟美國合作抗疫，好快大陸就算畀人日屌夜屌，連自己友都唔夠用都要一車車物資送過去"},{"pid":"eba5098bb7235fdf9776f2ed224a1d278a9f2544","tid":1954524,"uid":75767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:46:19.000Z","msg":"屌當初美國比物資你地咪又係厭三厭四"},{"pid":"24a92d60e2d693c42ca8b993283c328027be2169","tid":1954524,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c5484a8dea4cc7229a7a921602a2e4d67529c7a8","tid":1954524,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:21:55.000Z","msg":"原來係大慈善家 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n14蚊賣口罩比人  好撚有善心呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}